---
permalink: "/index.html"
layout: base.njk
title: "Polished map UI for your qgis2web exports"
extraHead: |
  <style>
  body { background: var(--q2w-surface); color: var(--q2w-text); }

  /* Top nav */
  .ln-nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--q2w-surface) 85%, transparent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
    padding: 14px 32px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;
  }
  .ln-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .ln-brand__mark { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--q2w-accent); color: var(--q2w-accent-fg); display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 12px; }
  .ln-version { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); padding: 2px 6px; border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-xs); }
  .ln-nav__links { margin-left: auto; display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: center; }
  .ln-nav__links a { font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 10px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); text-decoration: none; border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-xs); }
  .ln-nav__links a:hover { color: var(--q2w-text); background: var(--q2w-surface-soft); }
  .ln-brand__icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 6px; object-fit: contain; flex: 0 0 auto; }
  .ln-nav__toggle { margin-left: 12px; flex: 0 0 auto; }

  /* Wrap */
  .ln-wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }

  /* Hero */
  .ln-hero { padding: 96px 0 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; }
  .ln-hero::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 0; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1100px; height: 480px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--q2w-accent) 12%, transparent) 0%,
      transparent 58%);
    opacity: 0.75;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: -1;
  }
  .ln-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
    border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-full);
    background: var(--q2w-surface);
    color: var(--q2w-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .ln-eyebrow .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--q2w-success); }
  .ln-hero h1 {
    font-size: 64px; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
  }
  .ln-hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--q2w-accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .ln-hero p.sub { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }
  .ln-cta { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; }
  .ln-cta .q2w-btn { padding: 10px 18px; font-size: 13px; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  .ln-page a,
  .ln-page button,
  .ln-card {
    transition:
      color 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
      background-color 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
      border-color 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
      box-shadow 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
      transform 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition:
      opacity 0.5s var(--q2w-ease),
      transform 0.5s var(--q2w-ease);
  }

  .reveal.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }

  .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

  .ln-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--q2w-accent);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--q2w-shadow-lg);
  }

  .ln-card:hover .ln-card__name {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--q2w-accent);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .ln-hero .q2w-btn--primary {
    animation: btn-breathe 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes btn-breathe {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 color-mix(in srgb, var(--q2w-accent) 40%, transparent);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px color-mix(in srgb, var(--q2w-accent) 0%, transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    .ln-page a,
    .ln-page button,
    .ln-card,
    .reveal {
      transition: none !important;
    }
    .reveal {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
    .ln-hero .q2w-btn--primary {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  /* Code preview */
  .ln-code {
    margin: 56px auto 0; max-width: 720px;
    /* Terminal mock — always dark regardless of OS theme */
    background: #0f1520;
    color: #e4e7ec;
    border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-lg);
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 13px;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -20px rgba(15, 122, 120, 0.25), 0 8px 32px rgba(15, 21, 32, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid #1f2937;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .ln-code__bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937; }
  .ln-code__bar .d { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: #2a3344; }
  .ln-code__bar .lbl { margin-left: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; }
  .ln-code__bar .copy { margin-left: auto; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; padding: 3px 8px; border: 1px solid #2a3344; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; }
  .ln-code__body { padding: 18px 22px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-x: auto; }
  .tk-c { color: #6b7280; }   /* comment */
  .tk-k { color: #c5a3ff; }   /* keyword */
  .tk-s { color: #7dd3a3; }   /* string */
  .tk-n { color: #fbbf77; }   /* name */
  .tk-p { color: #6b7280; }   /* punct */
  .tk-a { color: var(--q2w-accent); }

  .ln-showcase { padding: 80px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }
  .ln-showcase__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: 280px;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .ln-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
    border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-md);
    background: var(--q2w-surface);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 2; }
  .ln-card__preview {
    position: relative;
    flex: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    --q2w-surface: #ffffff;
    --q2w-surface-soft: #f7f8fa;
    --q2w-text: #1b2230;
    --q2w-text-muted: #5b6577;
    --q2w-text-faint: #8a93a3;
    --q2w-border: #dde1e7;
    --q2w-accent-soft: #e6f3f2;
  }
  .ln-card__meta {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
  }
  .ln-card__name {
    font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--q2w-accent);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .ln-card__desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--q2w-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ln-showcase__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 2; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .ln-showcase__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 1; }
  }

  /* Sections */
  .ln-section { padding: 80px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }
  .ln-section__head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .ln-section__head .num { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .ln-section__head h2 { font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 12px; font-weight: 700; }
  .ln-section__head p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* Origin */
  .ln-origin { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: center; }
  .ln-origin h2 { font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 16px; font-weight: 700; }
  .ln-origin p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .ln-compare {
    border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
    border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--q2w-surface-soft);
  }
  .ln-compare__row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--q2w-border); }
  .ln-compare__cell { background: var(--q2w-surface); padding: 16px 18px; }
  .ln-compare__cell--a { background: var(--q2w-surface-soft); }
  .ln-compare__lbl { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .ln-compare__row + .ln-compare__row { border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }

  /* Roadmap */
  .ln-roadmap {
    border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
    border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ln-rm__row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 100px; align-items: center; padding: 16px 24px; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }
  .ln-rm__row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .ln-rm__v { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-text); }
  .ln-rm__title { font-size: 14px; }
  .ln-rm__title small { color: var(--q2w-text-muted); font-size: 12px; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
  .ln-rm__status { text-align: right; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); justify-self: end; }
  .ln-rm__status--done { background: rgba(31,138,76,0.12); color: var(--q2w-success); }
  .ln-rm__status--now { background: var(--q2w-accent-soft); color: var(--q2w-accent); }
  .ln-rm__status--next { background: var(--q2w-surface-soft); color: var(--q2w-text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }

  /* Footer */
  .ln-footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); padding: 48px 0 64px; }
  .ln-footer__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  .ln-footer h4 { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); margin: 0 0 14px; font-weight: 600; }
  .ln-footer ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .ln-footer a { color: var(--q2w-text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; }
  .ln-footer a:hover { color: var(--q2w-text); }
  .ln-footer__bot { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .ln-hero::before {
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center,
        color-mix(in oklch, var(--q2w-accent) 8%, transparent) 0%,
        transparent 52%);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .ln-hero h1 { font-size: 40px; }
    .ln-origin, .ln-footer__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ln-nav { justify-content: space-between; }
    .ln-nav__links { display: none; }
    .ln-nav__toggle { margin-left: auto; }
  }
  </style>
---

{% include "nav-landing.njk" %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="ln-hero">
  <div class="ln-wrap">
    <span class="ln-eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> v0.4 · brand-neutral · MIT</span>
    <h1>Beautiful UI for your <em>qgis2web</em> exports.</h1>
    <p class="sub">A lightweight CSS framework for Leaflet exports, with optional JS interactions, Tailwind tokens, WebGIS templates, and polished map UI components.</p>
    <div class="ln-cta">
      <a href="examples/choropleth.html" class="q2w-btn q2w-btn--primary q2w-btn--pill">
        See live example
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="docs.html" class="q2w-btn q2w-btn--pill">Browse components</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Code preview -->
    <div class="ln-code reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="ln-code__bar">
        <span class="d"></span><span class="d"></span><span class="d"></span>
        <span class="lbl">terminal · install</span>
        <span class="copy">copy</span>
      </div>
<pre class="ln-code__body" style="margin: 0;"><span class="tk-c"># 1. Install</span>
<span class="tk-n">npm</span> <span class="tk-k">install</span> <span class="tk-s">q2w</span>

<span class="tk-c"># 2. Drop into your qgis2web export's index.html</span>
<span class="tk-p">&lt;</span><span class="tk-k">link</span> <span class="tk-n">rel</span><span class="tk-p">=</span><span class="tk-s">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="tk-n">href</span><span class="tk-p">=</span><span class="tk-s">"q2w/dist/q2w.css"</span><span class="tk-p">&gt;</span>

<span class="tk-c"># 3. Add a header — that's it</span>
<span class="tk-p">&lt;</span><span class="tk-k">div</span> <span class="tk-n">class</span><span class="tk-p">=</span><span class="tk-s">"<span class="tk-a">q2w-header</span>"</span><span class="tk-p">&gt;</span> ... <span class="tk-p">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-k">div</span><span class="tk-p">&gt;</span></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Component showcase -->
<section class="ln-showcase reveal" id="showcase">
  <div class="ln-wrap">
    <div class="ln-section__head">
      <span class="num">02 · COMPONENTS</span>
      <h2>Built for thematic maps.</h2>
      <p>30+ pre-styled components. Click any preview to see usage and copy code.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ln-showcase__grid">
      <a href="docs/header.html" class="ln-card ln-card--lg reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a8c5e, #3f5e44);">{% include "previews/header.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-header</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Floating brand pill with logo, title, actions.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/popup.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c5d6c5, #7d9c7c);">{% include "previews/popup.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-popup</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Tabular feature attributes with accent header.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/layer.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2f7, #dbe3ec);">{% include "previews/layer.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-panel</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Layer stacks, toggles, sublayers, and opacity rows.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/legend.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f1e9, #ead8bf);">{% include "previews/legend.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-grad</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Sequential and diverging legend bars for thematic maps.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/search.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f6f9, #d9e7ef);">{% include "previews/search.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-search</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Search field with icon, placeholder, and result context.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/control.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #364152, #111827);">{% include "previews/control.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-control</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Reusable control buttons for zoom, reset, layers, and tools.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/toast.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5, #d1fae5);">{% include "previews/toast.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-toast</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Transient success and status feedback after user actions.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/basemap.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e9eef6, #cad7ea);">{% include "previews/basemap.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-basemap</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Basemap picker with thumbnail tiles and active state.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/compass.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f4f4f5, #d4d4d8);">{% include "previews/compass.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-compass</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Orientation indicator for rotated maps and advanced controls.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/modal.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937, #111827);">{% include "previews/modal.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-modal</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Welcome, help, and onboarding overlays with strong focus.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/sheet.html" class="ln-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #bfdbfe);">{% include "previews/sheet.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-sheet</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Mobile-first bottom sheets for compact map workflows.</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="docs/footer.html" class="ln-card ln-card--lg reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="ln-card__preview" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbe7d3, #9db393);">{% include "previews/footer.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta"><div class="ln-card__name">.q2w-footer</div><div class="ln-card__desc">Sticky map footer with attribution, powered-by, and live coordinates.</div></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Origin -->
<section class="ln-section reveal" id="origin">
  <div class="ln-wrap">
    <div class="ln-origin">
      <div>
        <span class="num" style="font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--q2w-text-faint); display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;">03 · WHY q2w</span>
        <h2>qgis2web is great. Its UI isn't.</h2>
        <p>qgis2web ships a working Leaflet map in seconds — but the layer control, popup, and chrome haven't really changed in years. Most teams end up rewriting them from scratch on every project.</p>
        <p>q2w fixes that once. Pre-styled components, a coherent token system, dark mode, and themes — all in a CSS file you drop in alongside the export.</p>
        <p>Inspired by <a href="https://github.com/AnmolSaini16/mapcn" class="cs-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mapcn</a>, but focused on Leaflet (because qgis2web exports there) and on the thematic-map use cases QGIS users actually build.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ln-compare">
        <div class="ln-compare__row">
          <div class="ln-compare__cell ln-compare__cell--a">
            <div class="ln-compare__lbl">Vanilla qgis2web</div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted);">
              <input type="checkbox" checked> <span style="font-family: serif;">Layer 1</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); margin-top: 6px;">
              <input type="checkbox" checked> <span style="font-family: serif;">Layer 2</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ln-compare__cell">
            <div class="ln-compare__lbl">With q2w</div>
            <div class="q2w-layer" style="font-size: 11.5px;"><span class="q2w-layer__check q2w-layer__check--on">✓</span><span class="q2w-layer__name">Land value</span><span class="q2w-layer__opacity">90%</span></div>
            <div class="q2w-layer" style="font-size: 11.5px;"><span class="q2w-layer__check q2w-layer__check--on">✓</span><span class="q2w-layer__name">Roads</span><span class="q2w-layer__opacity">100%</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ln-compare__row">
          <div class="ln-compare__cell ln-compare__cell--a">
            <div class="ln-compare__lbl">Popup</div>
